Class JSONUtils

    • org.octoprint.api.util.JSONUtils

  • public class JSONUtils
extends Object
    Author:
    rweber This is a helper class to create Java objects based on JSON returned results. Classes are loaded via reflection but must implement the JSONLoader interface.
